                Reply to Student</button>
            <button onclick="closeFbModal()"
                style="flex:1;padding:11px;background:#F3F0EC;color:#374151;border:1.5px solid #E8E3DD;border-radius:10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">Close</button>
